SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE ([f].[IsDelete] = 0) AND ([f].[UserId] = @__userId_0)

SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]

    ELSE N'Two Way'

SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE ([f].[IsDelete] = 0) AND ([f].[UserId] = @__userId_0)

    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]

    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE

    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]

INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]

    ELSE N'Two Way'

END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE ([f].[IsDelete] = 0) AND ([f].[UserId] = @__userId_0)

SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE ([f].[IsDelete] = 0) AND ([f].[UserId] = @__userId_0)

    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE

END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]

SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]

SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE [f].[UserId] = @__userId_0

SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE [f].[UserId] = @__userId_0

SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE ([f].[IsDelete] = 0) AND ([f].[UserId] = @__userId_0)

SELECT [a].[FlightNumber], [a0].[AirlineNmae] AS [AirlineName], [a].[FromPlaceName] AS [FromPlace], [a].[ToPlaceName] AS [ToPlace], [a].[FlightStartDateTime] AS [DepartureTime], [a].[FlightToDateTime] AS [ArrivalTime], [f].[TotalCosts] AS [TotalCost], CASE
    WHEN [f].[Journey] = 0 THEN N'One Way'
    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE ([f].[IsDelete] = 0) AND ([f].[UserId] = @__userId_0)

END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
FROM [FlightBookingDetails] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [AirlineFlightDetails] AS [a] ON [f].[FlightId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AirlineDetails] AS [a0] ON [a].[AirlineId] = [a0].[AirlineId]
WHERE ([f].[IsDelete] = 0) AND ([f].[UserId] = @__userId_0)

    ELSE N'Two Way'
END AS [Journey], [f].[ClassStatus], CASE
    WHEN [a].[FlightStartDateTime] <= GETDATE() THEN CAST(0 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(1 AS bit)
END AS [CancalStatus], [f].[PNR] AS [PnrNumber], [f].[TotalBookSeats] AS [TotalSeats]
